p.k: Level A: Here and There is an educational programme that reveals interesting facts and tells about different events. The host of the programme uses easily understandable language. The viewers at these levels have no difficulty in following the presenter’s speech. The show can help you boost your vocabulary.
p.d: In this episode, we’re going to the wonderful city of Munich. The city has lots of attractions for all ages and tastes. But, there is one place where you always want to go back to. And this is The Odeonsplatz, the historical square in the center of Munich.
